Package: jSDM
Type: Package
Title: Joint Species Distribution Models
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2019-01-11
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.0), coda
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo, RcppGSL
NeedsCompilation: yes
