         comment=c(ORCID="0000-0002-1685-4997")))
Maintainer: Ghislain Vieilledent <ghislain.vieilledent@cirad.fr>
Description: Package for fitting joint species distribution models (jSDM)
    in a hierarchical Bayesian framework. The Metropolis-within-Gibbs algorithm 
    is written in C++, making use of Rcpp, Armadillo and GSL to maximize
    computation efficiency.
